{"id":511301,"date":[{"year":1971,"month":7,"day":11}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"庆祝中国共产党诞生五十周年,敬祝毛主席万寿无疆","genre":"","count":"175","ytitle":"","mtitle":"红心向阳放春辉","ftitle":"","authors":["路鸿"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方红造船厂　路鸿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在船台望北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红心向阳放春辉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁锤噹噹响云天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一锤一声多清脆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"焊花灿灿映星河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一朵一簇开红梅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷敲战鼓雨洗面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霜染衣衫雪当盔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咱为毛主席造大船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干劲胜似东海水!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨轮集队闹大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺破青天十万桅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舒卷长空万里霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饱蘸五湖三江水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十万船桅当彩笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大书:“毛主席万万岁!”"}]}